title: Rust compiler panicked unexpectedly

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body:
This change caused the error:
https://github.com/peterjoel/parity/commit/6ad224db1e1a5ee1b00840ae059cf60f71c0910a
## Meta

```
release: 1.8.0-nightly

```
